OL,3,C'They destroyed me': Palestinian Oscar
OL,4,Cwinner recalls attack by Israeli
OL,5,Csettlers
OL,7,FHamdan Ballal, who won an Academy
OL,8,FAward three weeks ago, said Israeli
OL,9,Fpolice beat him outside his home in
OL,10,Fthe village of Susiya on Monday, while
OL,11,Fofficers filmed the assault.
OL,13,FHe and two other Palestinians, who
OL,14,Fwere also attacked, were then arrested
OL,15,Fby Israeli troops who said they had
OL,16,Fbeen throwing stones.
