OL,3,C'They destroyed me': Palestinian Oscar
OL,4,Cwinner recalls attack by Israeli
OL,5,Csettlers
OL,7,FITV News Senior International
OL,8,FCorrespondent John Irvine spoke with
OL,9,FMr Ballal on Tuesday after he left the
OL,10,Fpolice station in the West Bank
OL,11,Fsettlement of Kiryat Arba where he was
OL,12,Fbeing held.
OL,14,FMr Ballal had bruises on his face and
OL,15,Fblood on his clothes, as he limped
OL,16,Finto the A&E department.
OL,18,F"They came, the soldiers with the
OL,19,Fsettlers attacking me and beating me
OL,20,Fand destroyed me," he told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
