OL,3,C'They destroyed me': Palestinian Oscar
OL,4,Cwinner recalls attack by Israeli
OL,5,Csettlers
OL,7,F"I don't know what I am feeling now,
OL,8,Fbut that's my home.
OL,10,F"So if I'm scared, afraid? Yes, maybe,
OL,11,Fthese feelings especially about my
OL,12,Ffamily, about my kids. But anyway, I
OL,13,Fwill be back to my home, because this
OL,14,Fis my home."
OL,16,FSitting on a hospital bed, while he
OL,17,Fwas undergoing medical tests, Mr
OL,18,FBallal explained how he has suffered
OL,19,F"hard" attacks since he picked up the
OL,20,Faward.
