OL,3,C'They destroyed me': Palestinian Oscar
OL,4,Cwinner recalls attack by Israeli
OL,5,Csettlers
OL,7,FITV News also spoke to Mr Ballal's
OL,8,Fwife, Lamia, who said her husband's
OL,9,FOscar has led to "intensified" attacks.
OL,11,F"The award has changed a lot," she
OL,12,Fexplained. "Ever since, the attacks
OL,13,Fhave intensified and his life is now
OL,14,Funder threat since he won."
OL,16,FThe Israeli military said Monday it
OL,17,Fhad detained three Palestinians
OL,18,Fsuspected of hurling rocks at forces
OL,19,Fand one Israeli civilian involved in
OL,20,Fwhat it described as a violent
OL,21,Fconfrontation.
