OL,3,C'They destroyed me': Palestinian Oscar
OL,4,Cwinner recalls attack by Israeli
OL,5,Csettlers
OL,7,FMr Ballal and the other directors of
OL,8,FNo Other Land, a documentary about the
OL,9,Fstruggles of Palestinians under
OL,10,FIsraeli occupation, took to the stage
OL,11,Fat the 97th Academy Awards in Los
OL,12,FAngeles earlier this month when the
OL,13,Ffilm won Best Documentary.
OL,15,FLea Tsemel, the lawyer representing
OL,16,Fthe three men, said they received only
OL,17,Fminimal medical care for their
OL,18,Finjuries and that she was denied
OL,19,Faccess to them for several hours after
OL,20,Ftheir arrest.
