OL,3,C'They destroyed me': Palestinian Oscar
OL,4,Cwinner recalls attack by Israeli
OL,5,Csettlers
OL,7,FPalestinian residents say around two
OL,8,Fdozen settlers - some masked, armed,
OL,9,Fand in military uniforms - attacked
OL,10,Fthe village of Susiya on Monday
OL,11,Fevening as residents were breaking
OL,12,Ftheir fast for Ramadan.
OL,14,FThey said soldiers who arrived pointed
OL,15,Ftheir guns at Palestinians while
OL,16,Fsettlers continued throwing stones.
