OL,3,C'They destroyed me': Palestinian Oscar
OL,4,Cwinner recalls attack by Israeli
OL,5,Csettlers
OL,7,FIsraeli police said Tuesday that the
OL,8,Fmilitary had handed over three
OL,9,Fsuspects for investigation on charges
OL,10,Fof rock-throwing, property damage, and
OL,11,F"endangering regional security".
OL,13,FThe three were released on condition
OL,14,Fthat they have no contact with others
OL,15,Finvolved in the case.
